two portals student, company

Student 
Home page - register as student button (opens up sign up page)
Sign up: Full Name, Batch, current CPI, Techstacks, age, gender,resume, email, password
Login: email,password
update student, delete

Filter on basis of :   1.batch    2.CPI    3.Techstacks
- Student can register in that company (sign up details)


Company
Home Page - resgister as company (opens up sign up page)
Sign up/Add company: Company name, official website, email, password, criteria (batch+teckstaks+cpi)
Login

update company, delete company

can see details of interested students (can mail directly to student if interested)







